Glock - a simple analog clock using GTK+
Copyright 2005, 2006 Eric L. Smith <eric@brouhaha.com>
$Id: README 16 2006-02-21 00:08:20Z eric $

Glock is a simple analog clock program using GTK+, and Cairo if it is
available (GTK 2.8 or later).

The original purpose of glock was to have a simple demo of an undecorated
non-rectangular window using gtk_widget_shape_combine_mask(), moveable
with the mouse using gtk_window_begin_move_drag().

